      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under documented version control with regression test suite; all simulation scripts archived in project repository.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under institutional license with documented version control. Simulation input files and post-processing scripts archived in the project Git repository with tagged release. Regression test results for the hemolysis power-law model confirmed against published benchmark cases."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must pass at least one published benchmark for rotating machinery internal flow; hemolysis sub-model must reproduce published analytical or reference solutions.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verified against the FDA critical path benchmark for pipe flow and backward-facing step. The power-law hemolysis model implementation verified against the Giersiepen analytical reference solution. No code modifications were made; standard solver settings applied."
