      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor; iterative convergence monitoring sufficient.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, explicit quantification of numerical solver error beyond iterative convergence monitoring is not required. Residuals converged to 1e-5 for all equations; mass imbalance < 0.01%. No further assessment performed."
    },
    {
