      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by a second qualified CFD analyst prior to production runs. Standard operating procedures for ANSYS Fluent rotating machinery simulations followed. Formal use-error quantification not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; model form selection documented and justified by literature precedent.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model and power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen coefficients) selected based on literature consensus for centrifugal blood pump applications. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2; selection justified by reference to FDA critical path guidance and peer-reviewed precedent."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
