      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; input parameters documented with sources and nominal values.",
      "rationale": "All model input parameters (fluid properties, boundary conditions, hemolysis model coefficients) documented with sources in the simulation report. Nominal values used throughout; probabilistic input uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2. The informal screening sensitivity study confirmed that ±10% variation in viscosity and ±2% variation in rotational speed produced less than 3% change in predicted NIH, supporting the adequacy of nominal inputs."
    },
