      "rationale": "Experimental validation data sourced from Hariharan et al. (2011), a multi-laboratory FDA-sponsored study using standardized bovine blood samples. Sample characterization (hematocrit, viscosity, source) documented in the original publication. Statistical analysis of inter-laboratory variability not required at MRL 2."
